{"tid":1326163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"714後有班沙田區議員俾藍絲網上政治攻擊","createTime":"2019-07-17T06:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T08:50:56.000Z","uid":21707,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"643d6961aae9a74bead7f2bb92592a590fd5fcf5","tid":1326163,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"714沙田遊行，天未黑就發生警民衝突.<br />\n有睇live既可能記得，有班人坐咗係最前線 緩衝防暴同示威者，咁果班人就係沙田區議員同立法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圖圈區議員許銳宇</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQQAVxz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQQAVxz.png&h=aab2c5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">圖為深夜時份沙田區議員記招</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9PufE2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9PufE2.png&h=d613f89e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日先講其中一個俾人搞既議員<br />\n<br />\n許銳宇當日一直都有著黃背心既<br />\n然後係佢fb就出現大量藍絲攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留言就問佢點解扮記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚麼乎有恐嚇留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/17/131931_e513e68cff0b7c3c583270a4d2a0cc24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F17%2F131931_e513e68cff0b7c3c583270a4d2a0cc24.png&h=34222386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文滙報</span>官方認證</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/498VVGY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F498VVGY.png&h=dc0bb71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多了，仲想了解既巴絲打請去沙田區政fb Page <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/134055657191138/posts/435546377042063/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F134055657191138%2Fposts%2F435546377042063%2F&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=670657cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/134055657191138/posts/435546377042063/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EKxX8S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EKxX8S.png&h=bea50f0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8c162356952d1de47021547504a35e5e3231b3b","tid":1326163,"uid":7517,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"藍絲班撚樣不知所謂"},{"pid":"ce8e8be2f7bf9548237918e070e56bc89ca2ca48","tid":1326163,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509a94ec3b5c5262edeaddb47991e8f724e8bda4","tid":1326163,"uid":89763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味"},{"pid":"9ae753e284e7dc84b8a36b830e869b04164d3015","tid":1326163,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:53:11.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"5373f0f38f0a2572f47a6c00e91700c55932222e","tid":1326163,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">fb ig wtsapp telegram<br />\n個個都要做文宣！！！！<br />\n出個post都唔肯既我馬上屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"bbbad2e3265c7392c8f18c6bbe957dd9294d95cd","tid":1326163,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}